data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!!!!!!!!!A stunning residence nestled in the desirable neighborhood of Stafford, Virginia. This impeccably maintained home offers a harmonious blend of modern elegance and comfortable living. Set on a spacious lot, this property presents a wonderful opportunity for those seeking a luxurious and serene lifestyle. As you approach the home, you'll appreciate the inviting exterior, featuring well-manicured lawns and beautiful landscaping. Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of natural light that bathes the interior, creating an airy and welcoming atmosphere. The open concept design seamlessly connects the main living areas, providing an ideal flow for both entertaining and everyday living. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, which is a chef's dream. It boasts high-end stainless-steel appliances, elegant granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and a convenient center island. Whether you're preparing a quick meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure to impress. The spacious living room serves as a versatile space for relaxation and gathering with loved ones. Large windows frame picturesque views of the surrounding greenery, infusing the room with an abundance of natural light. The primary suite is a tranquil retreat, offering a peaceful haven to unwind. It features a generously sized bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and double vanity. The remaining bedrooms are well-appointed, providing comfort and privacy for family members or guests. They share access to beautifully designed bathrooms that boast modern fixtures and finishes. Step outside and discover the private backyard oasis, a perfect setting for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or simply enjoying the tranquility of the surroundings. Picture yourself hosting barbecues, playing games, or relaxing on the patio on a sunny afternoon. Additionally, the home enjoys a convenient location with easy access to schools, shopping centers, restaurants, and major highways, ensuring a seamless commute. Schedule a showing today and envision the endless possibilities this remarkable property has to offer.
